snippet.title: Toasterball - How To Play
snippet.description:
How to play Toasterball ? Let's check out this ancient video we found on the subject.



Steam Page : https://store.steampowered.com/app/1142810/Toasterball/Toasterball is a multiplayer sport game (2-4 players), where you play as toasters. It's packed with crazy physics, random gameplay variants, explosions, and a bunch of toasts for you to burn!



The game was made by two guys, Alex and Simon, and woah, that's us! This is our Youtube page, but also feel free to check us out on Twitter (https://twitter.com/CouchGameCraft) and of course, check out the game!


Here's the link again : https://store.steampowered.com/app/1142810/Toasterball/



♥ Have a great day!
